snippet.title: GDC 2006 Project Offset
snippet.description:
Read More about this and other topics at http://www.ProjectOffset.com

We have weekly topics, were we discuss the different Offset technologies, and other cool topics too.

We have a "user submitted content" section, where you have chances to see your work, run through the Offset Editor!

Make sure when you visit us you sign up, and invite your friends -- you may find yourself winning something in one of our raffles.


We look forward to having you join us :)


Have a Great Day!


http://www.projectoffset.com
